{"tid":1566691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（急！！）全港最大型社工學生聯同社福界集會上線喇！！","createTime":"2019-09-13T16:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T16:46:41.000Z","uid":159380,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"607b039a099964f9cb2cf7072feb84aa31a586e9","tid":1566691,"uid":159380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:56:50.000Z","msg":"社福界一直同一眾香港市民同行<br />\n其實一班社工學生都係！！<br />\n面對社會既不公義 <br />\n我地更堅決要捍衛社工既價值<br />\n捍衛心中既價值觀<br />\n守護我地既良知 <br />\n我地要向呢個港共極權表示 <br />\n我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>絕對唔會向佢妥協</strong></span><br />\n我地呢班社工學生縱然面對白色恐怖 都<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">堅決與香港人同行</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n香港社會工作學生聯會將會喺<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月16號1430-1730喺愛丁堡廣場</span></span></strong>舉辦<br />\n「拒絕噤聲 凝伙結伴」集會 <br />\n（不反對通知書正在申請中）<br />\n<br />\n希望大家到場支持 聲援一班社工學生！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我願榮光歸香港</span></strong>"},{"pid":"3e8d458f110842550b4fbbf61bfda6eedb71a01e","tid":1566691,"uid":275285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:58:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"792fa79c20b5044184cb0dedfc2e61acb89ed991","tid":1566691,"uid":275285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"781126a05cc77498a85233d7fde7a28528db890f","tid":1566691,"uid":215345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T16:59:58.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"0d7ca74950163a37e3fbaca933e719f609875208","tid":1566691,"uid":232590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:00:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4f1a662a4735221c78bfd3ea5f5d69423b79ca6","tid":1566691,"uid":275285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T17:01: